<view class='headTop'>
  <avatar class="xl round" style="background-image:url({{userHeadIcon}})"></avatar>
  <view class="flex-sub padding-lr padding-tb-lg" bindtap="showModal" data-target="QrModal">
    <view class="text-lg">{{userName}}
      <tag class="round sm margin-left-sm" style="background-color: #f4d57a;" wx:if="{{userYearType===1}}">
        <text class="text-brown">年卡会员</text>
      </tag>
    </view>
    <view class="margin-top-sm">ID:{{userId}}</view>
  </view>
</view>
<view class='padding'>
  <view class='qrBox'>
    <image src='{{src}}' mode='widthFix'></image>
  </view>
</view>
<view class='padding text-center'>
  <view class='text-red'>分享二维码，邀请好友一起加入U乐空间</view>
  <view class="padding text-content text-sm">将二维码发送给好友，邀请好友进入小程序，成为U乐空间会员，可领取佣金</view>
</view>
